                        <p class="placename">
                Blechhammer<br /><span class="alt">(Auschwitz IV)</span>
            </p>
                            <p class="subcamp_of">
                <strong>Subcamp of: </strong>
                Auschwitz
            </p>
                                    <div>
                Established in April 1942, this camp was mainly peopled by Jews from Upper Silesia.
            </div>
